title: There Are No Bad Heroes In This World
alternative_titles: There Are No Bad Heroes In This World
There’s No Such Thing as a Bad Hero in the World
summary: There Are No Bad Heroes In This World Manhwa There’s No Such Thing as a Bad Hero in the World, 세상에 나쁜 용사는 없다 A man once hailed as the world’s strongest, the heavyweight champion of the largest fighting league, Choi Hyunseok, begins a new life as a hero in another world after his death. “A hero who has it all—wealth, honor, beautiful women!” With dreams of a glorious future, he crosses over to this new world, only to be greeted by a towering, muscular monster with the head of a bull. The monster, an officer in the Demon King’s army, sneers, “Hero? You’re supposed to be a hero?” “Uh… I think so…?”
